[NVL #43A] SDL2 and WebGPU in Emscripten: A Beginner's Guide (Part 1)

The Lone Engineer
The Lone Engineer
293 Abonnenten
Herunterladen
672 Aufrufe 04.05.2024
Welcome, fellow adventurers, to our thrilling journey into the world of WebGPU! Get ready to embark on an exciting exploration as we guide you through the creation of a minimal WebGPU application, versatile enough to be compiled either as a native desktop app or as a dynamic WASM module, ready to run right in your web browser! This tutorial is divided into two parts, and today, we're diving into the first segment. Our focus? Setting the stage for success by harnessing the power of SDL2 within the Emscripten environment. While this initial step may not directly involve WebGPU, it lays a crucial foundation for our upcoming adventures. So, fasten your seatbelts and prepare for an exhilarating ride!
